statements: SELECT * FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE genotype = 'AA';
SELECT variant_id, chromosome, nucleotide_change FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE allele_frequency > 0.5;
SELECT position, allele_frequency FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE chromosome = 'X';
SELECT variant_id, genotype, disease_risk_prediction FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE position BETWEEN 1000 AND 2000;
SELECT chromosome, position, disease_risk_prediction FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE genotype = 'CC' ORDER BY position DESC;
SELECT variant_id, chromosome, position, nucleotide_change, genotype FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE genotype='AA' ORDER BY variant_id DESC LIMIT 10;

SELECT chromosome, position, allele_frequency, disease_risk_prediction FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE allele_frequency > 0.5 AND disease_risk_prediction < 0.2 ORDER BY chromosome ASC, position DESC;
SELECT * FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE nucleotide_change LIKE '%del%' AND allele_frequency BETWEEN 0.1 AND 0.5;
SELECT position, disease_risk_prediction FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE genotype='CC' AND (chromosome='X' OR chromosome='Y') ORDER BY position ASC;
SELECT variant_id, allele_frequency FROM genomic_variation_data WHERE nucleotide_change='A>T' ORDER BY allele_frequency DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT model_name, algorithm, accuracy FROM Machine_Learning_Models WHERE trained_on > '2022-01-01';
SELECT model_id, model_name, algorithm, accuracy FROM Machine_Learning_Models ORDER BY accuracy DESC;
SELECT * FROM Genomic_Variations;
SELECT variation_id, chrom, ref, alt FROM Genomic_Variations WHERE position > 10000 ORDER BY position DESC;
SELECT G.chrom, G.position, D.disease_name, D.prediction FROM Genomic_Variations G JOIN Disease_Predictions D ON G.variation_id = D.variation_id WHERE D.prediction > 0.8;

SELECT M.algorithm, M.accuracy, M.trained_on, G.chrom, G.position, D.disease_name FROM Machine_Learning_Models M JOIN Disease_Predictions D ON M.model_id = D.prediction_id JOIN Genomic_Variations G ON G.variation_id = D.variation_id WHERE M.accuracy > 0.9 AND D.prediction > 0.5 ORDER BY M.trained_on DESC;

SELECT G.chrom, G.position, M.model_name, D.disease_name, D.prediction FROM Genomic_Variations G JOIN Disease_Predictions D ON G.variation_id = D.variation_id JOIN Machine_Learning_Models M ON D.prediction_id = M.model_id WHERE M.accuracy > 0.8 AND D.prediction < 0.3 ORDER BY D.prediction ASC;
